oot cause — nerve compression and muscle shutdown — the therapies work regardless of how long you’ve been suffering.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGBgdMGN1b_text","label":"ggGBgdMGN1b_text","default":"<p>Some people notice relief after the very first session. Most report feeling lighter, looser, and less stiff within the first week, with major improvements showing by the 2–3 week mark when used consistently for 15 minutes a day.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5779-Q2LD_text","label":"gg5779-Q2LD_text","default":"<p>Not at all! Just strap it comfortably around your lower back, choose your mode, and press start. The adjustable fit works for all body types, and the simple controls make it easy to relax while the belt does the work.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrcqOh_tmz_text","label":"ggrcqOh_tmz_text","default":"<p>Absolutely. You don’t need to do any special exercises or positions. The belt does the heavy lifting — decompressing your spine, restoring blood flow, and reactivating muscles — all while you’re sitting, lying down, or even lightly moving around the house.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text","label":"ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text","default":"<p>You’re fully covered by our 90-day money-back guarantee. Try the SmoothSpine Therapy Belt daily for three months. If you don’t feel a noticeable difference, simply send it back for a full refund — no questions asked.</p>"}],
